	scores : [0, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0],

	skills : ["Athletics"],

	skillstxt : "Athletics and any 1 skill",
	
	trait : "Vanara (+2 Dexterity, +1 Intelligence)\nI am proficient in the Athletics skill. Whenever I make a Strength (Athletics) check to climb, I add double my proficiency bonus to the check, instead of my normal proficiency bonus.\nI have a prehensile tail.\nThe Vanaras' intelligence and curiosity allows them to learn and pick up useful skills they would need in their lifetime. I gain proficiency in one skill of my choice and one proficiency in one tool of my choice."

